						a(href="https://github.com/cookbenjamin/saasplate" target="_blank") Code
					td
						a(href="http://benjamincook.io:3000" target="_blank") Demo
				tr
					th PolyPy
					td A library that automates polynomial regression analysis to find the ideal model with minimal effort.
					td(colspan=2)
						a(href="https://github.com/cookbenjamin/polyPy" target="_blank") Code
